msgid ""
"layout: post\n"
"title: Monitoring Quarkus apps using Micrometer and Prometheus into OpenShift \n"
"date: 2021-03-15\n"
"tags: extension\n"
"synopsis: Expose Quarkus Apps metrics into OpenShift using Micrometer and Prometheus\n"
